# Copy this file to `.env` (same directory) and fill in your keys.
# All Vite env vars must be prefixed with `VITE_` to be exposed to the browser.
# Restart `npm run dev` after editing.

# All upstream API keys (MML, OpenCellID, N2YO, FMI) live in backend/.env.
# The backend proxies tiles at /api/tiles/mml/... and data at /api/layers/...
# This file is kept for any future browser-only config.
